REACT PROPS
------------

    - Props is generally known as "properties" it sharing to one component to another component
    - Parent to child communication. all data should be passed on object strcture in props keyword


STEP 1 : Create a two FC components. one is parent component another one is child component.

 Component 1
------------
     
    function Home() {

        return <>

            <h1> Home page </h1>
            
        </>
    }


Component 2
------------
     
    function AboutUs() {


        return <>
            <h1> About page </h1>                   
        </>
    }


STEP 2 : Parent component inside which component called  that is called child component.

Component 1
------------
     
    function Home() {

        const [name,setName] = useState('Saravanan')

        return <>
            <h1> Home page </h1>
            <AboutUs />                      // Child component
        </>
    }


Component 2
------------
     
    function AboutUs() {
        return <>
            <h1> About page </h1>
                              // Child component
        </>
    }




STEP 3 :  Parents components states is pass to child component in custom attributes way

Component 1
------------

function Home() {

        const [name,setName]           = useState('Saravanan')
        const [age,setName]            = useState(27)
        const [hobbies,setHobbies]     = useState(['eat','dance','singing'])

        let caseStudyList = [ 
            {
                year : "2020 to 2021 ",
                work : 'TCS'

            },
            {
                    year : "2021 to 2022",
                    work : 'CTS'

            },
            {
                year : "2023 to 2024",
                work : 'wipro'

            },
        ]


        const [caseStudy,setCasestudy] = useState(caseStudyList)



        return <>

            <h1> Home page </h1>

            <AboutUs 
                name = {name}   // Child component
                age = {age}
                hobbies = {hobbies}
                caseStudy = {caseStudy}
            />                      
        </>
    }


  Every props value getting into Object Strcutre. 



Component 2
------------
     
    function AboutUs(props) {

       const  {name,age,hobbies,caseStudy}  = props                           // Destcturing

        return <>
            <h1> About page  </h1>
            <p> Candidate Name : {props.name} </p>
            <p> Candidate age :{props.age} </p>

            <h2> Hobbies list </h2>

            {hobbies &&
                hobbies.map((value,index) => {
                    return <p> {value}</p> 
                })
            
            }

            <h3> Employee Case study </h3>


             {caseStudy &&

                caseStudy.map((value,index) => {

                    const { year, work } = value

                    return (<React.component>

                        <p> working Period :  {year} </p>
                        <p> worked Company : {work} </p>


                    </React.component>)

                })
            
            }

        </>
    }









    






